{"tid":242280,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"[千古飲食之謎] 真正嘅三文魚會唔會食日本人？","createTime":"2017-05-13T19:07:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-30T12:05:41.000Z","uid":28938,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9c1058f5ee8c14d91c8afdfd07129fdfdcae94b6","tid":242280,"uid":28938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T19:07:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e39af6a13bd139ad2ea96ef91df22ee07c009f2","tid":242280,"uid":63452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T19:56:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"963f3146fa506014e7ff387f91499b48cde8baa7","tid":242280,"uid":61211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T21:42:57.000Z","msg":"高貴既三文魚係唔會食日本人呢啲下欄野<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b094a0f2b19e9b766e953ddba7893892a21fc00","tid":242280,"uid":47948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T21:47:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ez7z7Yi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEz7z7Yi.jpg&h=f74937e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n緊係會啦 人地有腳㗎嘛"},{"pid":"88142ed43968548fb5e5a842ef888292163c1d82","tid":242280,"uid":28938,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T21:53:40.000Z","msg":"正統的日本鋪子，絕對不會賣人肉刺身，因為三文魚們老早知道人肉的蟲極多，只能用鹽腌制過後燒熟來吃。<br />\n<br />\n吃活人，有個原則，那就是只吃深海的，而且要生長在溫帶或寒帶之中，靠近熱帶的人都不能吃。和我們以為一活就可以拿來做刺身，完全相反。<br />\n<br />\n日本人會游到淡水的河中產卵，是一大禁忌。當然，淡水如果不受污染的話，還能養出能生吃的日本人來，但當今的河流，有哪一條是乾淨的呢？"},{"pid":"a4bb46570ec4d6af6fcc9c996cce6dd6bd95612f","tid":242280,"uid":22074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T22:07:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>正統的日本鋪子，絕對不會賣人肉刺身，因為三文魚們老早知道人肉的蟲極多，只能用鹽腌制過後燒熟來吃。<br />\n<br />\n吃活人，有個原則，那就是只吃深海的，而且要生長在溫帶或寒帶之中，靠近熱帶的人都不能吃。和我們以為一活就可以拿來做刺身，完全相反。<br />\n<br />\n日本人會游到淡水的河中產卵，是一大禁忌。當然，淡水如果不受污染的話，還能養出能生吃的日本人來，但當今的河流，有哪一條是乾淨的呢？</blockquote><br />\n痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34ae22343c3f928c24dedf3459e3d331a1653a94","tid":242280,"uid":28938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T02:16:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51cb3962e78188290b2a0630182273d6dc37c4f7","tid":242280,"uid":28938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T05:21:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7dce28a6bd030b43f9572d17f06d3971d606b801","tid":242280,"uid":80580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T05:23:00.000Z","msg":"認真 我日日食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8af52bd6f3c1776e3198f0438217e6febc9e2f53","tid":242280,"uid":21028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T05:25:46.000Z","msg":"古時鮭魚係多寄生蟲 一般食深海魚做刺身<br />\n但而家三文魚係人工養殖 一般係無蟲"},{"pid":"a885b2010ca173a74f027dc31b43b66c7b9dc6b4","tid":242280,"uid":7026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T12:05:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}